Everything in Kubernetes goes through the
Kubernetes API Server.

Example command:

kubectl get pods

Flow:

kubectl
   │
   ▼
API Server
   │
   ├─ Authentication
   ├─ Authorization
   ├─ Admission Controllers
   │
   ▼
etcd


---

